name: INTERAIR PTY. LTD.
about: Interair Pty. Ltd. is a reputable flight training institution offering a comprehensive range of aviation programs. Our fleet includes single-engine, multi-engine piston, and multi-engine turbine aircraft, such as the Cessna 172, Cessna 182, Piper Seminole, Piper Navajo, and Beechcraft King Air B200. We provide training for Recreational Pilot Licence (RPL), Private Pilot Licence (PPL), Commercial Pilot Licence (CPL), and instrument flight rules (IFR) training. Our state-of-the-art aircraft are equipped with Garmin 430 GPS systems and both analogue and glass cockpit options. With a focus on safety and quality instruction, Interair ensures that students receive the best possible training to succeed in their aviation careers. Our experienced instructors and diverse fleet make us an ideal choice for aspiring pilots.
services:
